---
import Link from './Link.astro';
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section class="animate-onscroll gap-y-8 lg:flex-row lg:justify-between lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-0" id="about">
  <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-center lg:items-start">
    <div class="w-fit">
      <div class="flex justify-between">
        <h3 class="text-md text-gray-500 md:text-lg lg:text-xl">#</h3>
        <h3 class="text-md text-gray-500 md:text-lg lg:text-xl">02</h3>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-center text-xl text-gray-700 lg:text-right lg:text-3xl">About Me</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-y-12 md:w-10/12">
    <p class="text-center text-md text-gray-500 md:text-left lg:text-lg">
      Diligent Software Engineer, armed with 2 years of focused experience. Mastery in JavaScript, TypeScript, React,
      Angular, and Tailwind reflects my commitment to precision. Driven by a principle of continuous learning, I
      approach each project with a disciplined mindset. Every line of code is a deliberate step toward robust solutions.
      Let's craft a future where reliability meets innovation!
    </p>
    <Link arrow href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gphariyono/" target="_blank" class="text-md text-gray-600 lg:text-lg">
      Visit my Linkedin to know more
    </Link>
  </div>
</Section>
